rmangal 0.4.0
=============
* internal changes to the gestion of URL parameters
* filtering is now done within the `list***` functions rather than with a special function

rmangal 0.3.1
=============
* fixed bugs introduced by the switch from rjson to jsonlite in httr without breaking backwards compatibility
* optimized the patch and post function to decrease the number of API calls (we already have the URI of the requester)
* removed the internal function to get a list of resources, this is done directly by reading the API root

rmangal 0.3.0
=============
* Added functions to release a dataset (and all objects attached to it)

rmangal 0.2.1
=============
* Bug fix due to changes in how json objects are rendered by the parser

rmangal 0.2.0
=============
* Now uses API keys instead of usr/password
* `signUp` deprecated, login now needs to be done at http://mangal.uqar.ca/dashboard/

rmangal 0.1.1
=============
* It is now possible to filter the results using mangalSearch

rmangal 0.1.0
=============
* First complete release of the entirely usable package
* At this point, everything should be back-compatible

rmangal 0.0.1
=============
* First release on GitHub. Version Scheme: CRAN.MAJOR.MINOR. Unless MAJOR is at least 1, consider the package unstable.
